5 781 M
(RFC-025: Soup Query Language) s
5 759 M
(Status: Draft) s
5 748 M
(Date: January 2026) s
5 737 M
(Author: Derrell Piper <ddp@eludom.net>) s
5 726 M
(Implementation: Proposed) s
5 704 M
(------------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 682 M
(Abstract) s
5 660 M
(This RFC specifies the query language for the Library of Cyberspace soup: how principals ) s
5 649 M
(search, filter, and retrieve objects from the content-addressed store using the rich meta) s
5 638 M
(data layer. Queries are themselves content-addressed and auditable.) s
5 616 M
(------------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 594 M
(Motivation) s
5 572 M
(The soup contains infinite metadata. Finding needles requires a query language that is:) s
5 550 M
(- Expressive - Complex predicates, joins across objects) s
5 539 M
(- Efficient - Indexes, bloom filters, query planning) s
5 528 M
(- Secure - Queries respect capability boundaries) s
5 517 M
(- Auditable - Query patterns reveal access patterns) s
5 495 M
(Newton's soup had cursor-based queries. We extend this with content-addressed semantics.) s
5 473 M
(------------------------------------------------------------------------------) s
5 451 M
(Query Model) s
5 429 M
(Basic Queries) s
5 407 M
(;; Find by type) s
5 396 M
(\(soup-query type: 'document\)) s
5 374 M
(;; Find by attribute) s
5 363 M
(\(soup-query author: "alice@example.com"\)) s
5 341 M
(;; Find by multiple attributes \(AND\)) s
5 330 M
(\(soup-query type: 'document) s
5 319 M
(            author: "alice@example.com") s
5 308 M
(            created-after: "2026-01-01"\)) s
5 286 M
(;; Find by content hash) s
5 275 M
(\(soup-query hash: "sha256:7f83b1657ff1fc..."\)) s
5 253 M
(Query Results) s
5 231 M
(;; Results are lazy cursors) s
5 220 M
(\(define results \(soup-query type: 'document\)\)) s
5 198 M
(;; Iterate) s
5 187 M
(\(soup-cursor-next results\)    ; => soup-object or #f) s
5 176 M
(\(soup-cursor-peek results\)    ; => next without advancing) s
5 165 M
(\(soup-cursor-reset results\)   ; => back to beginning) s
5 143 M
(;; Collect \(careful with large result sets\)) s
5 132 M
(\(soup-cursor->list results\)   ; => list of soup-objects) s
5 121 M
(\(soup-cursor-count results\)   ; => total count) s
5 99 M
(Predicates) s
5 77 M
(;; Comparison operators) s
5 66 M
(\(soup-query size: \(> 1000000\)\)           ; larger than 1MB) s
5 55 M
(\(soup-query created: \(< "2025-01-01"\)\)   ; before 2025) s
5 44 M
(\(soup-query name: \(like "rfc-*"\)\)        ; glob pattern) s
5 33 M
(\(soup-query tags: \(contains "urgent"\)\)   ; list membership) s
5 11 M
(;; Logical operators) s
